Tango benchmarking harness

Usage: sleep_10[EXE] [OPTIONS] [COMMAND]

Commands:
  list     List benchmarks
  compare  Run paired benchmarking to compare two executables
  solo     Run a single benchmark in a solo (isolated) mode
  help     Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
      --color <COLORING_MODE>  [default: detect]
  -h, --help                   Print help
  -V, --version                Print version
